<p>
  <span class="nym">Poncia</span>
  <span class="gen">f.</span>
  
  <span class="etym">Fem. of <a class="nym" href="Ponce">Ponce</a>.
  </span>
  
</p>
  
  
<div class="def">
  <p>The name was rare outside of France.</p>
  
  


